eu.h2020.helios_social.modules.contentawareprofiling.data

Class ModelData

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.h2020.helios_social.modules.contentawareprofiling.data.ModelData
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CNNModelData, DMLModelData

    public class ModelData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the data relevant to each model that will be stored on the calculated profile. They consist of the Image objects on which the profile was calculated, the pre-calculated raw profile and intermediate model data that are necessary to facilitate more advanced usage scenarios, such as context aware profiling.
